          "reviewBody": "Don't know about others, but if you have sonal sachdeva as your ward's class incharge, you are blessed. She keeps super clear communication, regularly sends work accomplished last week, academic calander and other important circulars via emails and whatsapp as well.  I hope other class incharge also would be doing the same.  School overall is amazing, happy with that",
