            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "One of the most commendable aspects of Manav Rachna is its holistic approach to education. Beyond academics, the school places a strong emphasis on character building, emotional intelligence, and social skills. Through various extracurricular activities and interactive workshops, students are encouraged to explore their interests, develop their talents.\nFurthermore, teachers prioritizes individualized attention and personalized support for each student. Teachers take the time to understand the unique strengths, challenges, and aspirations of every child, ensuring that they receive the guidance and encouragement they need to reach their full potential. This personalized approach fosters a sense of confidence and self-belief in students, empowering them to overcome obstacles.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
